# 🦺 Ergonomic Risk Analysis System

> Real-time ergonomic risk detection for workplace safety 
> using computer vision and data analytics.

## Problem
Manual ergonomic assessments are time-consuming and subjective. 
This system automates posture analysis to detect risks in arm, 
back, and knee regions in real time.

## Approach
- Captured body joint angles using MediaPipe + OpenCV
- Classified risk levels (low / medium / high) based on angle thresholds
- Logged and analyzed data with Pandas + NumPy
- Reported findings through structured Excel outputs

## Key Results
- Tested in real-time simulation environment by 2 team members
- Joint angles measured with 90%+ accuracy
- Risk classifications validated across arm, back, and knee regions

## Tech Stack
`Python` `OpenCV` `MediaPipe` `Pandas` `NumPy` `Excel`
